snippet.title: DEFEND THE ISLAND! - Ships 3D Gameplay
snippet.description:
Ahoy pirates!

Ships 3D is an online naval warfare game featuring frantic frigate battles and chaotic smash-ups at sea. Join your friends in thrilling multiplayer ship wars featuring up to 80 players.

Ships 3D: https://yp3d.com/ships3d/
Discord: https://discord.gg/ZzZAUkbKyX
